{"tid":1739693,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李國能：對人大法工委就高院判決表態感擔憂","createTime":"2019-11-19T16:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T00:37:43.000Z","uid":20933,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"83960977c7c6dc4148d3b023cc47b3f84b30212d","tid":1739693,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:19:40.000Z","msg":"終審法院前首席法官李國能發表聲明，指人大法工委的聲明似乎認為，香港法院無權以不符合基本法為由，將香港法律裁定為無效。若確為這個意思，情況令人驚訝及擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n李國能說，自1997年，香港法院一直維持這種已擁有的權力，同時完全接受人大常委會，對香港具有約束力的任何解釋，人大常委會在1999年及之後的釋法，沒有作出其他的建議。<br />\n<br />\n李國能指，全國人大常委會只能在特殊情況下解釋《基本法》，並應避免在法庭頒下判決後作出詮釋，否則會對香港司法獨立帶來負面影響」"},{"pid":"991c2ee3a917ff15bf2c05ea9840368ca1905d3a","tid":1739693,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:19:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1214370&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1214370%26csid%3D261_341&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqIRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=99912b9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1214370&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"2261da1f18892d0d7289b30c372947e94a08ff8c","tid":1739693,"uid":309753,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:25:02.000Z","msg":"你班法律撚都係時候認真現實啦，仲以為香港有法治？"},{"pid":"0dae012d40dfa84f04f6fc464d106b55b2a32098","tid":1739693,"uid":55955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:31:01.000Z","msg":"終於知啦咩"},{"pid":"d7e81ed0baab01466b6b29addba8cb2b190679b3","tid":1739693,"uid":85169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:35:26.000Z","msg":"第二段既意思係咪話為左佢地法官既權力就扮睇唔到"},{"pid":"45af4fe3c61499769b7fea0bde7705265e0afb3c","tid":1739693,"uid":1751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2261da1f18892d0d7289b30c372947e94a08ff8c","tid":1739693,"uid":309753,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"